# Vercel Speed Insights Configuration - Already Implemented

## Summary
Upon investigation, Vercel Speed Insights has already been installed and configured in this project according to the latest official documentation from https://vercel.com/docs/speed-insights/quickstart.

## Current Implementation Status

### 1. Package Installation ✅
- `@vercel/speed-insights@2.0.0` is installed in `package.json` dependencies
- Package successfully installed and verified with `npm list @vercel/speed-insights`

### 2. React Integration ✅
**File: `lifespent/src/App.tsx`**
- SpeedInsights component imported from `@vercel/speed-insights/react`
- Component properly integrated in the App component
- Implementation follows official React/Vite documentation exactly

```typescript
